#### Commands




- 33: Write
	- 0100: Power Off
	- 0101: Power On
	- 04: Brightness
		- 1%:  01
		- 100% 64
	- 0504: Set Scene
		- 00: Sunrise
		- 01: Sunset
		...
	- 051501: Segment Color Mode
		- 00FFFF 0000000000 3200: RRGGBB padding Number of segments


- AA: Get Value
	- 01: is_on (Keepalive)
		- On:  AA0101
		- Off: AA0100
	- 04: get_brightness
		- 1%: AA0401
		- 100%: AA0464
	- 05: Get Mode
		- 0407: Scene Mode Scene 7 romantic

	- 06:   get_device_fw_version
		- Version: 3.02.24
	- 0703: hw_version
		- Version: 3.01.01
	- 0e: ???
		- ???: 0f
	- 11: ???
		- ???: 001e0f0f
	- 12: ???
		- ????: 00640000800a
	- 23: Current Colors?
		- Red: 0000000080
	- 40: ???
		- ???: 000f
	- a3: ???
		- ???: 01
	- a5: Number of Segments
		- 1501: 15 Segments starting at 01
	- a501: Get Segment 1
		- 64ff8d0b 64aa5511 64ff8d0b: (Brightness | Red | Green | Blue) 15 segments
	- a502: Get Segment 2
		- 64ff8d0b 64aa5511 64aa5511
	- a503: Get Segment 3
		- 64ff0000 64ff8d0b 64ff8d0b		
	- a504: Get Segment 4
		- 64ff8d0b 64ff8d0b 64ff8d0b
	- a505: Get Segment 5
		- 64ff8d0b 64ff8d0b 64ff8d0b
	- b1: Auth_key? 
		- No data
	- ee: ???
		- ???: 000a01
	- ff: ???
		- No data
